# --- Supabase (server-only: JWT validation for /api/admin/* including eTime sync) ---
# MUST match the same Supabase project as the website build (VITE_SUPABASE_URL).
# Production website (indus-erp.in): wbyzhknaqcjqqtwopupl — staging: xjzhlbpgnpcmbdlufhwo. Never mix.
# Live check: curl -s https://indus-erp.in/api/health → supabase_project must be wbyzhknaqcjqqtwopupl
# and service_role_key must be "ok". If supabase_project is xjzhlbpgnpcmbdlufhwo, Raw Attendance 401s.
# Do NOT set ERP_ENV=staging on the production API host.
# Staging hosts MUST set ERP_ENV=staging so production auto-pin does not rewrite their URL.
# If SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY is missing or from another project, Sync eTimeOffice returns 401.
# Dashboard → Project Settings → API (service_role is secret — never put in VITE_*).
